window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>One set of enemies has been dealt with, and Tad has made his way to a new town with a new shop. He's made some great friends and found a happiness he didn't know existed.</p> <p>If only life were that simple. His heritage is pushing into his life and choices will have to be made. That and those who want a piece of him have become even more powerful.</p> <p>Will he ever find the quiet life he wanted so much? Although, perhaps the bigger question is whether that's still the life he wants?</p>"; 
